{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6e0ef0fcf6","title":"周恩来对开封武斗问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"afb0b70b49","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":5,"articleId":"6e0ef0fcf6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fdd5a1c389","type":"title","text":"周恩来对开封武斗问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6e0ef0fcf6"},{"id":"3d847ec230","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6e0ef0fcf6"},{"id":"336f4cfd5e","type":"paragraph","text":"九月四日晚九时以后，老保先后对我仪表、空分、阀门、拖电等厂进行骚扰袭击，叫喊要消灭六零九三和造反派，并冲击我高压阀门厂，使用黄色炸药。一军杨政委和杜副军长先后向周总理反映了这一情况。九月五日上午八时四十五分，河南省军区党委办公室秘书组周成继同志来电：总理很关心开封问题。总理指示我们向老保明确指出：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6e0ef0fcf6"},{"id":"0938b26d22","type":"paragraph","text":"“必须立即停止进攻，放下武器，得到保护。消灭造反派和驻军是反革命行动。”","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6e0ef0fcf6"}],"page":{"id":"8418086bab","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6e0ef0fcf6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}